-- Digital Pioneers Plans Mobile Application for IPhone
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-03-13T20:40:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-13/digital-pioneers-plans-mobile-application-for-iphone.html
Digital Pioneers NV will introduce
a new mobile application that allows users to sell furniture,
books and other items over the iPhone.  Called Stuffle, the application to be introduced this
spring will connect sellers and potential buyers within a 5-
kilometer (3 mile) radius, Heiko Hubertz, the majority owner of
Digital Pioneers, said at an event in Hamburg today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
